Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.87,0:00:05.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦  动作快点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:07.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透在等你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.31,0:00:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.13,0:00:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有落下东西吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.53,0:00:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.50,0:00:16.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.94,0:00:19.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.72,0:00:25.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  小伦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.82,0:00:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.18,0:02:00.90,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,300)\be1}下雨天就来泡澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.82,0:00:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？是那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:12.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？昨天晚饭后我发过信息给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.57,0:02:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没看到那条信息哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:18.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？小伦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.71,0:02:19.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.79,0:02:20.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的袜子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.09,0:02:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.09,0:02:27.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了穿另一边的袜子了  呜呜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好丢脸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话还不如光脚走呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.60,0:02:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.11,0:02:46.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小…小伦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:48.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:50.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你内裤呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.66,0:02:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.26,0:02:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我连这都没注意到也实在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:00.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我实在是太没脑子了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:02.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要蹲下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:03.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会从前面看到的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:05.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太困了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:08.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是那样的理由吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:11.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连这种事情都会有吗  真的吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:11.38,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的  谁都会有落下的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.14,0:03:14.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然内裤不是普通的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.61,0:03:16.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透  刚才…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.04,0:03:21.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你一定认为我没有内裤了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.07,0:03:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伦  不要跑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:31.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又这样了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:33.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透也真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.64,0:03:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉呢  透
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢  就只有早上比较糊涂…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太困了  迷迷糊糊的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.63,0:03:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题在那里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:49.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经穿上了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  说得也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:55.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是以为说不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:57.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  伦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.44,0:03:58.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.02,0:04:03.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天下午的课堂笔记能借我抄一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这么说来你昨天早退了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.38,0:04:08.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哟  给你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.55,0:04:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么语言？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.09,0:04:20.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦  是日语哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.81,0:04:23.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上课的时候我被睡魔侵袭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:25.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不只是早上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:27.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点潦草吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:30.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没有那回事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.11,0:04:33.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.32,0:04:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有看不清的地方的话  就要问我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.01,0:04:36.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:38.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.02,0:04:42.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  优子  等下也借我看看哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.12,0:04:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系哟  抄完了的话就给伦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:51.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.66,0:04:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.71,0:04:55.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.53,0:04:56.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚是近视眼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.12,0:04:58.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,视力有多少呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.79,0:05:03.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2.0  这只是装饰眼镜罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？为什么要戴装饰眼镜？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不戴的话…就会看到一些不该看到的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.27,0:05:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  你说的…莫非是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.36,0:05:19.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  现在在优子的背后…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.12,0:05:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  只是胡说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:24.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:26.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了只是玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:28.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:31.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个值得一耍的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.13,0:05:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是近视眼罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.78,0:05:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的别再吓我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.34,0:05:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我对这种恐怖的事情最没辙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.79,0:05:39.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也吓了一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.92,0:05:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小渚的演技真好  都能进话剧部了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是话剧部的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:46.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.73,0:05:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是幽灵部员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.26,0:05:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.73,0:05:50.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…才怪！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.84,0:06:11.44,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}出自夏目漱石的短篇小说「心」  下文翻译为中文原版翻译
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.84,0:06:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「这个夏天  我收到你二三封信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得确实是第二封信  你托我在东京找个适当的工作…」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:09.92,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想去厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.53,0:06:14.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:18.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  想去厕所什么的太丢脸了我说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  我的头好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.39,0:06:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子  你捂的是肚子！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊也不是  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.77,0:06:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.55,0:06:40.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去厕所  我带优子去保健室然后顺带去一次可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:42.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  优子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.39,0:06:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:52.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉啊  伦  真是帮了大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:55.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  因为我也想去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:57.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  伦也想去厕所？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:06:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:04.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保健室…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.47,0:07:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦  你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.12,0:07:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里不舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:16.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不知道怎么回事  但是很难受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是犯了什么病…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:21.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去…去厕所吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.06,0:07:23.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  还是保健室？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  厕所  厕…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:28.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厕…厕…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:32.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}首字母发音都是TO
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:32.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  应该是透啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:35.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子  你搞错了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.96,0:07:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.82,0:07:41.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦  振作起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.12,0:07:46.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦她突然失去意识了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天保健室老师也不在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:54.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.63,0:07:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来  去联络别的老师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:07:59.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两人  都安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.90,0:08:00.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.30,0:08:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.83,0:08:10.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是睡眠不足而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.60,0:08:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没带伞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.69,0:08:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:39.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上明明是晴天的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.96,0:08:41.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这也只是小雨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.15,0:08:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑回家的话没关系吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.22,0:08:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  透
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:55.44,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}雨女即百鬼夜行中能呼风唤雨的神，现在也指外出即下雨的女性。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:55.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近我发现了…我其实是雨女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.11,0:08:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把身体伸出去啦  快点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:03.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  湿透了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.33,0:09:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是乱来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.98,0:09:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁啊  猥琐地盯着这边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为小伦现在都这副样子了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:20.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.15,0:09:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:23.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.37,0:09:32.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:37.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这所学校  真好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.57,0:09:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伦  必须快点擦干
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.66,0:09:47.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞  完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.18,0:09:49.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透  穿着这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.22,0:09:50.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:53.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锵！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.06,0:09:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就不需要打伞了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都这个年纪了穿这个有点紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是小学生的话那就另当别论了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  确实是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:06.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿情侣装确实有点不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:06.48,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}翻译：小伦把きつい的意思理解错了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  就只一个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:10.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是那个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.29,0:10:17.06,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就不穿了  反正我也完全淋湿了 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:13.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.56,0:10:16.06,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:18.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:19.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.44,0:10:21.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小渚  优子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离我远点！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:30.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  还以为你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:32.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦  你湿透了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.71,0:10:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家很近  去我那里烘干吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是还在下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.82,0:10:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是在学校里面住着雨女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.01,0:10:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.28,0:10:51.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是暴雨  只要快点跑就好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:55.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都湿了就不可怕了呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.02,0:10:56.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.10,0:10:59.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  如果只是去渚家的距离…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不爽…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:03.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想被淋湿  叫个出租车好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.48,0:11:06.53,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}日本的出租车费用是世界上最贵的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.48,0:11:06.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做着不像高中生该做的事！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:11.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等会儿的话  会不会停呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:12.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:14.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说叫个出租车…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.58,0:11:17.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走喽  小渚的家在这边吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.66,0:11:18.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.63,0:11:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.23,0:11:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！等等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:26.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  别丢下我！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.27,0:11:26.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.84,0:11:30.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨什么的明明会使人忧郁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.30,0:11:31.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们却那么开心的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.70,0:11:35.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是青春啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.45,0:11:47.02,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,80)\fad(500,0)}鬼\N头\N老\N师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.09,0:11:47.02,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(620,70)\fad(300,0)}爱\N好\N：\N写\N诗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.39,0:11:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了  下雨了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.02,0:11:48.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(40,90)}诗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:51.82,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,80)}现\N实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.92,0:00:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.70,0:11:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:11:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  请进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊快去洗澡吧去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.46,0:12:05.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？大哥已经回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚  原来你有哥哥的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥  现在朋友来我家了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.01,0:12:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要占用盥洗室哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小渚是称呼哥哥为大哥的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.41,0:12:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是称呼他为哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大哥啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.83,0:12:30.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  浴缸一次只能容纳两人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分成2个组吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备  石头剪子布
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.62,0:12:39.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我和伦先去洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.71,0:12:42.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们换衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.04,0:13:06.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想起来才发现…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今还没和透单独聊过天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说点什么好呢  这种时候的沉默有点  有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.81,0:13:23.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:25.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉她们要洗很久
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.04,0:13:28.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有很多DVD
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.44,0:13:29.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说…说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.11,0:13:36.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「真正存在的恐怖都市传说」和继续沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要哪个呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.03,0:13:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是究极的选择…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.86,0:13:44.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  把衣服脱了放在那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.16,0:13:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  是这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:49.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快点钻进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:51.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  你是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？我是伦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.11,0:13:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  我知道的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:02.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一根刘海…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以改变一个人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:13.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.28,0:14:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这反应…腻了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.24,0:14:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.70,0:14:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个人都清爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.32,0:14:29.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  不洗快点她们就没法洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.12,0:14:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是  不快点跟小透和优子交换的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.13,0:14:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我的房间里只有她们两个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.90,0:14:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:44.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的  因为她们很要好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.39,0:14:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  说起来也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了  不行了  再这样下去真不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.14,0:15:12.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对哦  把眼睛闭上就不可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:24.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我才想喊呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:27.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:29.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了快去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.89,0:15:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  优子  浴室空出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:37.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.27,0:15:39.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:41.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子  不好啦  优子石化啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.60,0:15:45.21,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.89,0:15:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好可怕啊  终于可以洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  透？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.73,0:15:54.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:15:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.45,0:16:11.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥  透你有没有过洗头时因为看不到前面而觉得很可怕的经历
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.52,0:16:19.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在小时候很不擅长用洗发露洗头的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗发露进眼睛了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:29.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什么鬼啊透
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:31.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喷头在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.54,0:16:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛不行啦…眼睛不行啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.08,0:16:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  优子  你们两个很吵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.99,0:16:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  不要啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.08,0:16:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我还以为自己要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:04.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意识开始朦胧了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:09.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伦  看  我看到绿洲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:12.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚  伦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:21.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子  浴缸的水温  如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.54,0:17:22.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  把暖气关掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:29.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把衣服烘干而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.84,0:17:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.39,0:17:37.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.33,0:17:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人担心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.21,0:17:42.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多都干了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.15,0:17:45.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨会不会马上停啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.86,0:17:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时还不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.12,0:17:50.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下的真久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨天就如头发一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.86,0:17:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的好像就是噼里啪啦一下子倒下来那种
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.16,0:17:59.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的是散开的  完全不会缠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.54,0:18:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为发质不一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.87,0:18:06.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我摸摸优子的头发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子的头发好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:15.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透  搞起吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.06,0:18:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  这衣服好看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.83,0:18:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要动哦  因为现在是关键时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:52.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们搞啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.19,0:18:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.09,0:19:01.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  输掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.61,0:19:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还想来一局？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要刷新渚的记录
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.88,0:19:09.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有干劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.27,0:19:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子的手指挺漂亮的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.19,0:19:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才没这回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时应该有修剪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有特别去弄过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.41,0:19:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.61,0:19:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很舒服  但是有点不好意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.88,0:19:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？透…等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.47,0:19:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我要怎么做才好嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:01.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:06.02,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}还是没有要停的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.24,0:20:07.79,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}下的可真久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.80,0:20:12.00,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}但是我还是很喜欢雨的声音的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.17,0:20:16.07,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}这种心情我也懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.08,0:20:17.13,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:21.02,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}好啦  渚  你也把眼睛闭上倾听雨声吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.22,0:20:25.32,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}哎…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.87,0:21:22.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实不坏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.81,0:21:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是总感觉听到什么烧起来的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:31.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉肚子饿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.13,0:21:32.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.24,0:21:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？是我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.69,0:21:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  回家路上小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.44,0:21:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  你还借我们伞真是谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.66,0:21:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天见了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.06,0:21:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.18,0:21:53.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.12,0:21:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  这伞真可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.11,0:22:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确啊  啊  雨还是好大
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.45,0:22:03.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下班电车是几点的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.81,0:22:09.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥  可以用盥洗室了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.03,0:22:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经说过  要你们路上小心点了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:24.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.12,0:00:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.52,0:24:02.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家久等了  下集柚多谷和美宝莲要登场了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.20,0:24:03.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.48,0:24:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来我苦守贞洁15年了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.26,0:24:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  人生回顾到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.43,0:24:10.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说我们好像在第一话里说过会出场的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.88,0:24:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这么说了也只会在OP里出现
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.03,0:24:15.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.87,0:24:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  A频道  同级生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.65,0:24:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不光是同级生  高年级组当然也是会登场的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.82,0:00:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------INJP-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.36,0:20:04.89,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放課後予定もなんもないし
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:09.74,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨が降ってるから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.74,0:20:12.34,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,うちに集合
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:20.19,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君は普段から素直じゃないけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:24.07,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日はきっと分かるはず
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:30.19,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑顔がみたいだけだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:40.09,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そんな所にかくれないでいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:43.99,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もっとほら近づいて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.99,0:20:47.69,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きみも友達だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.69,0:20:55.77,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これから何度も過ぎていく季節も
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:59.46,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ずっとほら近くにいて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.46,0:21:05.49,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きみと一緒にいたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.31,0:21:13.34,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きみと笑ってたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.82,0:00:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------INCN-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.36,0:20:04.89,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下课后没有任何活动的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:09.74,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为雨一直下着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.74,0:20:12.34,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来我家集合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:20.19,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你平时就不怎么率直
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:24.07,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我也一定可以明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:30.19,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是你的笑脸很像我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:40.09,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必躲藏在那个地方的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:43.99,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再让我们靠得更近些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.99,0:20:47.69,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.69,0:20:55.77,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来将要度过的各种季节
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:59.46,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会一直都在你身边的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.46,0:21:05.49,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你在一起哟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.31,0:21:13.34,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你一起欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.82,0:00:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------OPJP-------------------
